@startuml MFA Git Access CLI
!theme plain
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

actor "Developer" as dev
participant "MFA Git\nCLI" as cli
participant "AWS STS" as sts
participant "Git\nCredential\nHelper" as git
actor "Authenticator\nApp" as mfa

dev -> cli: mfa-git-auth
cli -> dev: Enter MFA code
dev -> mfa: Get code from\nauthenticator app
mfa --> dev: 6-digit code
dev -> cli: Provide MFA code

cli -> sts: AssumeRole\n(MFA code + ARN)
sts --> cli: Temporary credentials\n(access key, secret, session)

cli -> git: Configure credential helper\nwith temp credentials
cli -> dev: QR code (first-time setup)

dev -> git: git clone/push/pull
git -> dev: Transparent auth\n(no password prompt)

note right of sts
  Credentials expire
  after configured duration.
  Developer re-runs CLI.
end note

@enduml